------------------------------------------------------------
CONTRIBUTIONS AND DERIVATIVES
------------------------------------------------------------
Contributions to this repository (including new board designs, modifications,
or software updates) are welcome. All contributions are understood to be
licensed under the same terms as the corresponding section above (hardware or
software).

If you create a derivative uFerris-compatible board or firmware, please:
- Retain the attribution to "uFerris" and link back to this repository.
- Clearly indicate your modifications.
- Use the same CC BY-SA 4.0 (for hardware) and MIT (for software) licenses
  when redistributing.

------------------------------------------------------------
PROJECT INFORMATION
------------------------------------------------------------
This project aims to support open and accessible embedded Rust learning
hardware. For details and updates, visit:

